snippet.title: The Imperial Realm :: Miranda - Bold New World Trailer
snippet.description:
The Imperial Realm::Miranda is an open-world massively multiplayer real-time strategy game in the tradition of Command and Conquer™. Fight either by yourself, or with your friends, in an all-out war to dominate Miranda, the devastated former capital of The Imperial Realm.

Bold New World is the third update to The Imperial Realm::Miranda and a major upgrade to the art and rendering engine.

Learn more at http://theimperialrealm.com

Music is Franz Schubert Piano Sonata no. 7 in E-flat major, D. 568 IV. Allegro moderato performed by Paul Pitman. Public domain: https://musopen.org/es/music/7264-piano-sonata-no-7-in-e-flat-major-d-568/
